Package com.example.networkmeup.view.SignUpTest.SignUpEmployerTest

Class SignUpEmployerViewStub

java.lang.Object
com.example.networkmeup.view.SignUpTest.SignUpEmployerTest.SignUpEmployerViewStub
All Implemented Interfaces:
SignUpEmployerView
public class SignUpEmployerViewStub extends Object implements SignUpEmployerView
This class represents a stub of the View component for the Employer Sign-Up process used in testing. It implements the SignUpEmployerView interface to simulate user interface actions and display feedback.
